## BNB Chain Integration Points

### 1. BNB Greenfield (Decentralized Storage)
**Bucket**: `shieldbot-reports`
**Network**: BNB Greenfield Mainnet
**Purpose**: Immutable storage of forensic reports for high-risk transactions
**SDK**: `greenfield-python-sdk`
**Report Format**: JSON objects stored at `https://greenfield-sp.bnbchain.org/view/shieldbot-reports/reports/<id>.json`

**Status**: ✅ Live and operational

### 2. BSC Mainnet RPC
**Network**: Binance Smart Chain (BSC)
**Chain ID**: 56
**RPC**: https://bsc-dataseed1.binance.org/
**Purpose**: Contract verification, bytecode analysis, transaction simulation
**APIs Used**: BscScan API, Web3 RPC calls

**Status**: ✅ Live and operational

### 3. opBNB Mainnet RPC
**Network**: opBNB (Layer 2)
**Chain ID**: 204
**RPC**: https://opbnb-mainnet-rpc.bnbchain.org
**Purpose**: Multi-chain contract scanning support

**Status**: ✅ Live and operational

