## How to Verify ShieldBot Integration

### 1. Greenfield Reports
Visit any report URL (example):
```
https://greenfield-sp.bnbchain.org/view/shieldbot-reports/reports/<report_id>.json
```

### 2. BSC RPC Calls
ShieldBot makes the following on-chain queries:
- `eth_getCode` - Contract bytecode retrieval
- `eth_call` - Token name, symbol, decimals, totalSupply
- Contract verification status via BscScan API
- Transaction history via BscScan API

### 3. Live Bot Testing
Test the live Telegram bot:
```
@shieldbot_bnb_bot
/scan 0x10ED43C718714eb63d5aA57B78B54704E256024E
```

---

## Notes

- **ShieldBot operates primarily off-chain** for real-time performance (<2s response time)
- **On-chain components** (ShieldBotVerifier) are optional for transparency, not required for core functionality
- **BNB Greenfield** provides decentralized storage without requiring smart contract deployment
- **All blockchain interactions are read-only** via RPC (no gas costs for users)

